casebody.data:
Larry Spencer HILL
v.
George KENWORTH. No. 435P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2006. Larry Spencer Hill, Pro Se. George Kenworth, Pro Se. Robert Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 18th day of August 2006 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, McDowell County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 18th day of August 2006."
